{"tid":1430982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[匿名軍校]   實戰經驗傳承   幫助所有人進化","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:57:23.000Z","uid":105976,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1094c8b5725c6b96986c4658d7c9ed220a7d7a4","tid":1430982,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"鑑於冇乜渠道可以安全分享夢遊經驗  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而對比起裝備  人員既實戰經驗先係最寶貴   </span></strong></span><br />\n所以整左個匿名 唔洗開ac 唔洗登入email既安全留言系統<br />\n等所有人都可以從實戰經驗中進化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等各位發完夢可以分享返重要經驗/提議<br />\n任何方面都可以講  心態/裝備/戰術/後勤/其他 etc<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeecLLdSFThCi1ZFsg7fmTlg_gPcqv0QGxqJVj6fpt7ZyyOVw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeecLLdSFThCi1ZFsg7fmTlg_gPcqv0QGxqJVj6fpt7ZyyOVw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f6b6a402\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeecLLdSFThCi1ZFsg7fmTlg_gPcqv0QGxqJVj6fpt7ZyyOVw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n^ google 表單  留言  唔洗email唔洗登入   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[軍工台] 7.8小更新 護目鏡&amp;頭盔&amp;手套更新數據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429744/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429744/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全防圖詳解&amp;購買連結 轉分頁 強烈建議睇 用pc開<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=aaf69daa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"b37ad9ae